metadata.name: You Can Trust Me
metadata.description:
a Bright and sunny day and we find ourselves inside.

We leave everything behind and explore the colors and emotions within.

We look at each other and see, we can create and enjoy and be free.

You can trust me, there is more to it, if you know about colors, you will know what I mean.

Look at it and see, You can Trust me.

Model: Zhiwei
Shot on film
35mm
Shanghai
2022
